Set of scripts and patches to convert a vanilla microk8s install to be IPv6 only.

Information and/or ideas compiled in part from:

https://discuss.kubernetes.io/t/microk8s-ipv6-dualstack-how-to/14507
https://github.com/sgryphon/kubernetes-ipv6
https://sgryphon.wordpress.com/2021/01/05/kubernetes-on-ipv6-only/
Kubernetes offical docs
Some internal know-how
